---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
import { Title } from '../components/title';
import { ViewTransitions } from 'astro:transitions';

---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body class="dark:bg-zinc-800">
		<Header title={SITE_TITLE} />
		<ViewTransitions />
		<main>
			<Title id="hello">üßë‚ÄçüöÄ Hello, Astronaut!</Title>
			<p class="dark:text-white">
				Welcome to the official <a class="dark:text-blue-600" href="https://astro.build/">Astro</a> blog starter template. This
				template serves as a lightweight, minimally-styled starting point for anyone looking to build
				a personal website, blog, or portfolio with Astro.
			</p>
			<p class="dark:text-white">
				This template comes with a few integrations already configured in your
				<code class="dark:text-zinc-800">astro.config.mjs</code> file. You can customize your setup with
				<a class="dark:text-blue-600" href="https://astro.build/integrations">Astro Integrations</a> to add tools like Tailwind,
				React, or Vue to your project.
			</p>
			<p class="dark:text-white">Here are a few ideas on how to get started with the template:</p>
			<ul>
				<li class="dark:text-white">Edit this page in <code class="dark:text-zinc-800">src/pages/index.astro</code></li>
				<li class="dark:text-white">Edit the site header items in <code class="dark:text-zinc-800">src/components/Header.astro</code></li>
				<li class="dark:text-white">Add your name to the footer in <code class="dark:text-zinc-800">src/components/Footer.astro</code></li>
				<li class="dark:text-white">Check out the included blog posts in <code class="dark:text-zinc-800">src/pages/blog/</code></li>
				<li class="dark:text-white">Customize the blog post page layout in <code class="dark:text-zinc-800">src/layouts/BlogPost.astro</code></li>
			</ul>
			<p class="dark:text-white">
				Have fun! If you get stuck, remember to <a class="dark:text-blue-600" href="https://docs.astro.build/"
					>read the docs
				</a> or <a class="dark:text-blue-600" href="https://astro.build/chat">join us on Discord</a> to ask questions.
			</p>
			<p class="dark:text-white">
				Looking for a blog template with a bit more personality? Check out <a 
					class="dark:text-blue-600"
					href="https://github.com/Charca/astro-blog-template"
					>astro-blog-template
				</a> by <a class="dark:text-blue-600" href="https://twitter.com/Charca">Maxi Ferreira</a>.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
